{"tid":2514020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"騙徒以違國安法為藉口  單一案件最高損失金額達220萬元","createTime":"2021-05-03T03:47:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T04:01:15.000Z","uid":354974,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"44287db066dd13be43fe93953797bde9288b7f47","tid":2514020,"uid":354974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:47:53.000Z","msg":"【騙徒以違國安法為藉口 受害人險失900萬】<a href=\"http://bit.ly/3aV8KTe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3aV8KTe&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOONdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=7e00664c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/3aV8KTe</a><br />\n<br />\n去年《港區國安法》生效至今年首季，警方共接獲15宗訛稱受害人違反國安法的 #騙案，受害人年齡介乎17至82歲，單一案件最高損失金額達220萬元，受害人是一名65歲的退休女士，暫時未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n在另一騙案中，一名71歲的陳女士上月接獲報稱是「中央電訊局」人員的來電，指控她在內地宣揚「港獨」，負責案件的長沙公安局要求她將900萬元轉入新開設的戶口協助調查，並需要交出網上理財密碼，以證清白。對方更發送印有陳女士照片的拘捕令，及向她轉賬合共4萬元為她支付提取定期存款罰款等費用，令她對騙徒深信不疑，最終銀行職員在她計劃提取900萬元時報警，陳女士未有損失。<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n【新聞專題﹕港區國安法】<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3etYW27\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3etYW27&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOONdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=da225f99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3etYW27</a><br />\n<br />\n#信報 #即時新聞 #港區國安法"},{"pid":"d53897ece9796e5bdd37cd74f835f487fc02a722","tid":2514020,"uid":165113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都估撚到有支那人囉嚟搵食 信個班荒死唔係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a49019ad9577b5d90ff006ab424c5fb531c0c9bc","tid":2514020,"uid":354974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T03:50:08.000Z","msg":"針對藍絲既騙徒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec440ebe464deec504e29b78f4a6be7dc8d2c686","tid":2514020,"uid":